let rec assoc (d,k,l) = 
match l with
[] -> d
| (b, a)::tail when b = k -> a
| _::tail -> assoc (d, k, tail)

let removeDuplicates l = 
let rec helper (seen,rest) = 
match rest with 
[] -> seen
| h::t -> 
let seen' = if List.mem h seen then seen
else
h::seen
in
let rest' = t in 
helper (seen',rest') 
in
List.rev (helper ([],l))
